	<h1 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-176668305" class="story-title"> <a   href="//science.slashdot.org/story/25/03/10/1851249/are-microplastics-bad-for-your-health-more-rigorous-science-is-needed">Are Microplastics Bad For Your Health? More Rigorous Science is Needed</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-025-00702-2"  title="External link - https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-025-00702-2" target="_blank"> (nature.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
		<!--<span class="comments commentcnt-176668305" >20</span>-->
		

		
		<!-- comment bubble -->
		
			<span class="comment-bubble"><a href="//science.slashdot.org/story/25/03/10/1851249/are-microplastics-bad-for-your-health-more-rigorous-science-is-needed#comments" title="">20</a></span>
		
	</h1>
	<div class="details" id="details-176668305">
		<span class="story-details">
		<span class="story-views">
			<span class="sodify" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better"></span><span class="icon-beaker pop1 " alt="Popularity" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')"><span></span></span> 
		</span>
		</span>
		<span class="story-byline">
	
				
			Posted
				by 
		
		
			
				  msmash
			
		
		

		
		
		<time id="fhtime-176668305" datetime="on Monday March 10, 2025 @02:51PM">on Monday March 10, 2025 @02:51PM</time>
		
		
